-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phi-2018-gia-su-mon-toan-lop-1-bat-mi-giai-phap-giup-con-hoc-tot\/#1_Tim_gia_su_day_mon_Toan_lop_1_cho_con_co_phai_la_qua_som\" >1. T\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1 cho con c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm?<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phi-2018-gia-su-mon-toan-lop-1-bat-mi-giai-phap-giup-con-hoc-tot\/#2_Vai_tro_cua_gia_su_day_mon_Toan_lop_1_o_Ha_Noi\" >2. Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1 \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phi-2018-gia-su-mon-toan-lop-1-bat-mi-giai-phap-giup-con-hoc-tot\/#3_Tim_gia_su_Toan_lop_1_bang_cach_nao\" >3.\u00a0T\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phi-2018-gia-su-mon-toan-lop-1-bat-mi-giai-phap-giup-con-hoc-tot\/#4_Bang_gia_gia_su_day_kem_mon_Toan_lop_1\" >4. B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phi-2018-gia-su-mon-toan-lop-1-bat-mi-giai-phap-giup-con-hoc-tot\/#5_Giao_vien_sinh_vien_day_kem_mon_Toan_lop_1_la_ai\" >5. Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean, sinh vi\u00ean d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1 l\u00e0 ai?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-left kksr-valign-top\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;1035&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;greet&quot;:&quot;\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 post&quot;,&quot;legend&quot;:&quot;0\\\/5 - (0 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;24&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;[H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed 2018] Gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1 - B\u1eadt m\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p gi\u00fap con h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;_legend&quot;:&quot;{score}\\\/{best} - ({count} {votes})&quot;,&quot;font_factor&quot;:&quot;1.25&quot;}'>\n            \n<div class=\"kksr-stars\">\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-inactive\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"1\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"2\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"3\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"4\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"5\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-active\" style=\"width: 0px;\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n                \n\n<div class=\"kksr-legend\" style=\"font-size: 19.2px;\">\n            <span class=\"kksr-muted\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 post<\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">Cha m\u1eb9 c\u00f3 bi\u1ebft, l\u1edbp 1 l\u00e0 l\u1edbp m\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 d\u1ea1y con, b\u1edfi l\u1ebd, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eddi con ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc. Thay v\u00ec con \u0111ang quen vi\u1ec7c \u0103n, ch\u01a1i, ng\u1ee7 ngh\u1ec9, hi\u1ec7n nay, con ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi s\u00e1ch v\u1edf, c\u00e2u ch\u1eef, con s\u1ed1. Kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y tr\u1ebb t\u1ecf ra th\u00edch th\u00fa, hay ch\u1ec9 th\u00edch th\u00fa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0i bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ed3i t\u1ecf ra m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, th\u00edch ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n. Do \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o cho con h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u qu\u00fd ph\u1ee5 huynh \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1 cho con. Trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 <strong>gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1<\/strong> c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, chuy\u00ean d\u1ea1y <strong>gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc<\/strong>,\u00a0n\u1eafm b\u1eaft v\u00e0 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u t\u00e2m l\u00fd h\u1ecdc sinh, \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng \u201cvi\u00ean g\u1ea1ch\u201d tri th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u201ctrang gi\u1ea5y tr\u1eafng\u201d.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1055 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/A\u0309nh-chu\u0323p-Ma\u0300n-hi\u0300nh-2018-09-28-lu\u0301c-4.01.43-CH.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"542\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/A\u0309nh-chu\u0323p-Ma\u0300n-hi\u0300nh-2018-09-28-lu\u0301c-4.01.43-CH.png 542w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/A\u0309nh-chu\u0323p-Ma\u0300n-hi\u0300nh-2018-09-28-lu\u0301c-4.01.43-CH-300x212.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 542px) 100vw, 542px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Tim_gia_su_day_mon_Toan_lop_1_cho_con_co_phai_la_qua_som\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\"><strong>1. T\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1 cho con c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">Ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1 kh\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ph\u1ee5 huynh, c\u00f2n vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c con ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">Hi\u00ean nay, ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, c\u00e1c b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh kh\u00f3 b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 d\u1ea1y cho con, do \u0111\u00f3, nhi\u1ec1u b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thu\u00ea gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 gi\u00fap con h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t ngay t\u1eeb ban \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">Ph\u1ee5 huynh b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho c\u00e1c con<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">Ph\u1ee5 huynh d\u1ec5 c\u00e1u g\u1eaft khi gi\u1ea3ng m\u00e3i m\u00e0 con kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u b\u00e0i =&gt; \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh t\u1ea1o t\u00e2m l\u00fd s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i, ch\u00e1n gh\u00e9t m\u00f4n To\u00e1n<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">C\u00e1c con h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 k\u00e8m b\u00e0i nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 gi\u00e1o th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng, v\u00ec tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u1ecdc sinh ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 t\u00e2m, l\u00fd s\u1ee3 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean h\u01a1n<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">Tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c em ch\u01b0a cao<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1057\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/day-kem-lop-1-1024x576-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/day-kem-lop-1-1024x576-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/day-kem-lop-1-1024x576-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/day-kem-lop-1-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">==&gt;&gt;\u00a0<em>Vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t <strong>gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1<\/strong>, c\u00f9ng ph\u1ee5 huynh k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p c\u00e1c b\u00e9 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u qu\u00fd ph\u1ee5 huynh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Vai_tro_cua_gia_su_day_mon_Toan_lop_1_o_Ha_Noi\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\"><strong>2. Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1 \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc c\u00f9ng <strong>gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m to\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1<\/strong> s\u1ebd gi\u00fap con b\u1ea1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi c\u00e1c con s\u1ed1, h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfm s\u1ed1, vi\u1ebft s\u1ed1 chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">\u00a0H\u1ecdc c\u00f9ng\u00a0<em><strong>gia s\u01b0 to\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1<\/strong><\/em><strong><em>,<\/em><\/strong> con b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00e9p t\u00ednh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, linh \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap con b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa h\u01a1n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng to\u00e1n h\u1ecdc l\u1edbp 1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc, con b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc v\u1ec1 sau n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng, gi\u00fap cho con b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n v\u1edbi to\u00e1n h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1056\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/giup-con-hoc-toan-lop-1-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/giup-con-hoc-toan-lop-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/giup-con-hoc-toan-lop-1.jpg 660w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\"><em>Gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n to\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn con l\u00e0m b\u00e0i t\u1eadp c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 t\u01b0 duy n\u00e2ng cao<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Tim_gia_su_Toan_lop_1_bang_cach_nao\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\"><strong>3.\u00a0T\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">&#8211; Tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn t\u1eeb b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1edd ng\u01b0\u1eddi quen.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">&#8211; T\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 tr\u00ean google, facebook, zalo&#8230;.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">&#8211; \u0110\u1ec3 nhanh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia s\u01b0 gi\u1ecfi, Qu\u00fd ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi <strong>trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh<\/strong> qua Hotline:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\"><span style=\"color: #333399;\">096.31.38.511 ho\u1eb7c ( 024 ) 62.54.1130<\/span>. \u0110\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00ecm <strong>gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1<\/strong> mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">Test tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ecdc sinh mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">H\u1ecdc th\u1eed 2 bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gia s\u01b0<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed5i gia s\u01b0 b\u1ea5t k\u00ec khi n\u00e0o gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi con m\u00ecnh<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">H\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u1ebb h\u01a1n<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p m\u1ecdi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n 24\/24<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-818\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su\u031b-ha\u0300-no\u0323\u0302i-300x114.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"228\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su\u031b-ha\u0300-no\u0323\u0302i-300x114.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su\u031b-ha\u0300-no\u0323\u0302i-768x292.png 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su\u031b-ha\u0300-no\u0323\u0302i.png 820w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><em>Gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh &#8211; Cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0 gi\u1ecfi, gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">==&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p TOP +500 <strong>gia s\u01b0 gi\u1ecfi<\/strong>, c\u00f3 nghi\u00eap v\u1ee5 s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m, cam k\u1ebft ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 trong 10 bu\u1ed5i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Bang_gia_gia_su_day_kem_mon_Toan_lop_1\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\"><strong>4. B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1<\/strong><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<table width=\"479\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\" width=\"479\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #282828;  font-size: 120%;\"><strong>H\u1eccC PH\u00cd GIA S\u01af M\u00d4N TO\u00c1N L\u1edaP 1<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>Sinh vi\u00ean<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>1 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">100.000 &#8211; 120.000<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">200.000 \u2013 250.000<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>2 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">150.000 &#8211; 180.000<\/span><\/td>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">250.000 &#8211; 300.000<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>&gt;= 3 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/span><\/td>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i, h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tu\u1ef3 theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng vui l\u00f2ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 hotline: 096.31.38.511 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: <strong>B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed gia s\u01b0<\/strong> t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c update m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018 &amp; nh\u1eadn ngay 2 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc th\u1eed.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Giao_vien_sinh_vien_day_kem_mon_Toan_lop_1_la_ai\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\"><strong>5. Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean, sinh vi\u00ean d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1 l\u00e0 ai?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau tr\u1ebb con<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 qua tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 T\u00e0i m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 T\u00e2m, ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c s\u00e2u r\u1ed9ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 l\u00f2ng y\u00eau ngh\u1ec1.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">C\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp cho b\u00e9<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">C\u00f3 th\u00e2m ni\u00ean gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p h\u1ecdc sinh. K\u1ecbp th\u1eddi n\u1eafm b\u1eaft n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00e2m l\u00ed ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y khoa h\u1ecdc d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u, kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u00e1p l\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 g\u1ee3i n\u00ean h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh v\u1edbi m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">\u00a0V\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a n\u1ec1n gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c hi\u1ec7n h\u00e0nh nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp cao nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1058\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/hopmat2016-300x197.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/hopmat2016-300x197.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/hopmat2016-768x505.png 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/hopmat2016-1024x673.png 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><em>Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean &#8211; Sinh vi\u00ean d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m m\u00f4n To\u00e1n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><i>\u00a0&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\"><strong><em>=&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c: <\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\"><strong><em>Gia s\u01b0 k\u00e8m l\u1edbp 1<\/em><\/strong><em>: To\u00e1n + Ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t + Anh l\u1edbp 1 &#8211; H\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, s\u1ebd gi\u00fap con v\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 sau.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/strong>: Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u00fap con h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t, cha m\u1eb9 y\u00ean t\u00e2m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><i>\u00a0&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng To\u00e1n cho b\u00e9 l\u1edbp 1 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm <strong>gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 1<\/strong> h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh th\u00f3i quen h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp cho b\u00e9, l\u00e0 ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1 cho qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp sau n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u00e9. Qu\u00fd ph\u1ee5 huynh h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7n ngay v\u1edbi <strong>trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh <\/strong>qua Hotline:\u00a0096.31.38.511 ho\u1eb7c ( 024 ) 62.54.1130\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\"><b>TRUNG T\u00c2M<\/b>\u00a0<b>GIA S\u01af<\/b>\u00a0<b>B\u00ccNH MINH<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 : T\u00f2a N03 &#8211; Ph\u1ed1 Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u00fd Ki\u00ean, Q.C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">Email: <a style=\"color: #282828;\" href=\"mailto:giasubinhminh.eduvn@gmail.com\"><span class=\"s2\">giasubinhminh.eduvn@gmail.com<\/span><\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 120%;\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7: 096.31.38.511 ho\u1eb7c ( 024 ) 62.54.1130<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Cha m\u1eb9 c\u00f3 bi\u1ebft, l\u1edbp 1 l\u00e0 l\u1edbp m\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 d\u1ea1y con, b\u1edfi l\u1ebd, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eddi con ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc. Thay v\u00ec con \u0111ang quen [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1036,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[464,478],"tags":[204,203,192,191,202,189],"class_list":["post-1035","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-gia-su-lop-1-mb","category-gia-su-mon-toan-mb","tag-day-kem-toan-lop-1",